    <!-- Application Structure Plan: A single-page, vertical scroll layout with a sticky top navigation. The structure is narrative-driven: it starts with a strong personal summary, moves to a chronological timeline of professional experiences, visually showcases a diverse skill set with interactive charts, and finishes with educational background and contact info. This design choice provides an intuitive and engaging user journey, making the content more digestible and memorable than a static document. -->
    <!-- Visualization & Content Choices: 
        - Ringkasan Diri -> Goal: Inform/Engage -> Presentation: Prominent hero text block -> Method: Static HTML/Tailwind -> Justification: To create a powerful first impression.
        - Pengalaman (Kerja & Mengajar) -> Goal: Show Change/Growth -> Presentation: Vertical timeline -> Method: HTML/CSS with Tailwind -> Justification: To visually represent the career journey chronologically.
        - Keahlian (Skills) -> Goal: Compare/Highlight -> Presentation: Two horizontal bar charts for Hard and Soft skills -> Method: Chart.js/Canvas -> Justification: To offer a quick, dynamic, and memorable visual comparison of the candidate's diverse abilities, including technical and creative skills.
        - Pendidikan -> Goal: Inform -> Presentation: Clean card layout -> Method: HTML/Tailwind -> Justification: To present foundational information clearly without distracting from the core skills.
    -->
    <!-- CONFIRMATION: NO SVG graphics used. NO Mermaid JS used. -->
